Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的飛龍？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易茲 才人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃亮登場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別閃亮吧 趕快飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼？快去追他們 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人 露易茲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有緣再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那天到來之前我們彼此都要活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 朱利奧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼你會？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是受阿尼艾斯所托 前來尋找你們二位的
